<item>
            <title>[LU-2351] tests: remote_node works wrong</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-2351</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;The test-framework remote_node works wrong for host names with any suffixes.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Example:&lt;br/&gt;
In 1-node configuration on node &quot;vm01&quot; run tests like mds_HOST=vm01 sh sanity.sh&lt;br/&gt;
If the node has any dns suffix, remote_mds() function will compare &quot;vm01&quot; with &quot;vm01.&amp;lt;suffix&amp;gt;&quot; and returns true even in 1-node case.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Xyratex ticket: MRP-629&lt;/p&gt;
</description>
